description: BioPower Operations Corporation, through its subsidiaries, focuses on operating HyFi Platform. The HyFi Platform is a proposed decentralized finances (DeFi) exchange marketplace using blockchain platform technology. Its DeFi marketplace offers non-fungible tokens, initial license offerings, bridge loan offerings, pre-special purpose acquisition company, pre-initial public offering funding, CeDeFi commodities exchanges, and membership programs. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Aventura, Florida.
